{"tid":993372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西九文化區地盤　發現輻射物質　","createTime":"2019-01-24T01:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T10:51:59.000Z","uid":6497,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1ba8c2e06c259639fe4865fccb5671426bf62660","tid":993372,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T01:19:24.000Z","msg":"西九文化區近擎天半島一個地盤，昨晚9時許，職員報警指懷疑發現輻射物質，消防接報到場，出動危害物質處理車及危害物質專隊人員，警方爆炸品處理組人員，亦有到場處理。機動部隊警員在場戒備。事件中無人受傷及毋須疏散。<br />\n據稱，地盤定期化驗泥土，今次化驗樣本於20米地底抽取，位於天秤附近，報告指泥土內有輻射物質，於是報警。至凌晨3時，警方爆炸品處理組人員及機動部隊離場。凌晨4時許，消防探測到地盤輻射在安全水平，收隊離場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190124/large/1548264483_15b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190124%2Flarge%2F1548264483_15b2.jpg&h=5172c7f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190124/large/1548265901_1071.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190124%2Flarge%2F1548265901_1071.jpg&h=00724787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190124/large/1548265523_6ca3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190124%2Flarge%2F1548265523_6ca3.jpg&h=fcc088cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190124/large/1548265513_61a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190124%2Flarge%2F1548265513_61a7.jpg&h=b90af598&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f960f9d59180efe5aa680ce93711750072fc856a","tid":993372,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T01:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93173d252df922ecbdcdf2660ea009cb6e4a85ec","tid":993372,"uid":72009,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy